<h2 style="color: #333; margin-top: 0;">Geciken Fatura Hatirlatmasi - {{invoiceNumber}}</h2>

<p>Sayin <strong>{{tenantName}}</strong>,</p>

<p>
  <strong>{{invoiceNumber}}</strong> numarali faturaniz icin odeme suresi
  gecmis bulunmaktadir.
</p>

<table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 16px 0;">
  <tr style="background: #f8f9fa;">
    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #dee2e6;"><strong>Fatura No</strong></td>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #dee2e6;">{{invoiceNumber}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #dee2e6;"><strong>Tutar</strong></td>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #dee2e6;">{{currency}} {{amount}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="background: #f8f9fa;">
    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #dee2e6;"><strong>Son Odeme Tarihi</strong></td>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #dee2e6;">{{dueDate}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #dee2e6;"><strong>Gecikme Suresi</strong></td>
    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #dee2e6;">{{daysOverdue}} gun</td>
  </tr>
</table>

<div style="background: #f8d7da; border-left: 4px solid #dc3545; padding: 12px; margin: 16px 0;">
  <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Lutfen en kisa surede odemenizi yapiniz.</strong> Odeme gecikmesi ek masraflara yol acabilir.</p>
</div>

{{#if hostedUrl}}
<div style="text-align: center; margin: 24px 0;">
  <a href="{{hostedUrl}}" style="background: #dc3545; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block;">
    Simdi Ode
  </a>
</div>
{{/if}}

<p>Saygilarimizla,<br>Havalimani Ticari Gelir Yonetimi</p>
